  "remarks": "Colonel Azatbek Asanbekovich Omurbekov, head of the 392nd Military Training Center, is the former commander of the 64th Separate Motorised Rifle Brigade of the 35th Combined Arms Army of the Russian Federation, which killed, raped and tortured civilians in Bucha, Ukraine. These atrocities constitute crimes against humanity and war crimes. He was awarded the title of Hero of Russia.",
